abstract:
The present invention checks the pavement road surface temperature and humidity conditions of the curve road or steep slope road (hereinafter referred to as &#34;accident area&#34;) zone, which is a high risk of traffic accidents, and determines the road surface condition based on the road surface temperature. Based on the signal, the recommended driving speed can be determined, and the road conditions and recommended driving speeds are displayed in real time to the driver who wants to proceed in this section, and the situation can be notified to the traffic situation room using the track. One accident-related area is a digital signage for road surface indication. 
     In particular, a digital sign board is installed on each side of the ramp in the accident frequent area section; 
     A temperature sensor and a humidity sensor installed in the pavement layer at intervals of the accident occurrence area at several intervals; 
     Collecting a signal input from the temperature and humidity sensor, and compares the detected detection signal with a predetermined reference data value to determine and deliver the determined signal to the digital scoreboard and traffic information integrated situation room Characterized in that it comprises an information collection device integrally.
